00:14:29.100 --> 00:14:34.280
When you become the Spirit, what happens to us -

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:42.660
to understand that we have to understand the nature of the Spirit.

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:49.420
Spirit is the reflection of God Almighty on our heart.

00:14:50.380 --> 00:14:55.220
We are the reflectors. These reflectors start

00:14:56.880 --> 00:15:03.780
working since we were stones, we can call them or matter, then living creatures,

00:15:04.740 --> 00:15:12.280
till we reach a state when we are human-beings, the Spirit is expressed

00:15:13.180 --> 00:15:17.540
in our heart, in the best way.

00:15:20.460 --> 00:15:27.500
But it is still in a witness state watching us all the time what we are doing.

00:15:29.520 --> 00:15:35.460
It doesn't come into our attention - He's just watching

00:15:38.080 --> 00:15:43.760
but when the Kundalini rises and pierces through your fontanel bone area -

00:15:45.160 --> 00:15:48.680
so this is the seat of the God Almighty

00:15:49.260 --> 00:15:53.400
and the reflection of the Spirit is in your heart.

00:15:54.360 --> 00:16:01.960
So first of all, it connects your brain with your heart, as a result

00:16:03.860 --> 00:16:11.780
a kind of a pulsation - in Sanskrit it's called as 'Spanda' - starts flowing

00:16:12.200 --> 00:16:19.400
on your Central Nervous System, which you can call it as cool vibrations.

00:16:20.340 --> 00:16:24.280
Also it is co-related

00:16:25.140 --> 00:16:30.340
with the All-Pervading Power which is

00:16:32.960 --> 00:16:38.020
flowing within our being because of this connection.

00:16:50.220 --> 00:16:57.780
The Spirit is the one that is the Absolute Truth.

00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:06.440
Absolute Truth means there is no other Truth than that.

00:17:08.640 --> 00:17:15.620
For example, if you have ten children and tie up their eyes

00:17:17.740 --> 00:17:23.100
and ask them, "What is the matter with this gentleman?"

00:17:24.220 --> 00:17:27.780
they will all raise the same finger. Supposing, there is this finger

00:17:30.500 --> 00:17:37.260
or this finger, any finger. Like the other day,

00:17:38.260 --> 00:17:43.900
somebody asked Me, "Mother, why they were they all asking, 'What is your relationship with your father?'"

00:17:45.960 --> 00:17:52.900
because there is indication on this finger, on the right hand

00:17:53.680 --> 00:18:01.200
that there's something wrong with the fatherhood. Either you are not a good son or he's not a good father; It could be even the husband.

00:18:03.600 --> 00:18:07.220
And you ask the gentleman, he'll be surprised that how do you know.

00:18:09.460 --> 00:18:15.280
So the Truth, which is Absolute, comes to you on your finger-tips.

00:18:18.220 --> 00:18:23.400
You immediately know what's wrong with the other person and what's wrong with you.

00:18:24.360 --> 00:18:30.560
Now you don't talk the language like English or Hindi, Marathi,

00:18:31.140 --> 00:18:36.020
Sanskrit but you speak the language of the centers. This is what happened

00:18:36.540 --> 00:18:42.000
when the disciples of Christ were blessed by Holy Ghost and they got their realization,

00:18:43.680 --> 00:18:51.060
that they started speaking the language of the centers. So you don't say that

00:18:53.760 --> 00:19:01.720
this center of yours is bad because you have got ego -

00:19:02.760 --> 00:19:08.580
you don't have to say that way. You just have to say that Agnya is not working alright.

00:19:09.640 --> 00:19:14.720
Sahaja yogis would come and tell Me, "Mother, please solve my problem of Agnya." "What's the matter?"

00:19:15.960 --> 00:19:23.280
"I can't bear it, it's a headache." So he doesn't see it as ego but he sees it as a

00:19:23.580 --> 00:19:29.640
causal of it. The cause of his headache is his ego

00:19:29.980 --> 00:19:37.140
and he sees it as Agnya chakra. So he comes and tells Me - actually if you see in short -

00:19:37.560 --> 00:19:41.400
it is, he says, "I've got too much ego, please remove it Mother from my head."

00:19:45.700 --> 00:19:52.160
So you reach that subtler state when you understand what is fundamentally, basically wrong with you

00:19:52.420 --> 00:19:59.060
because these are the fundamentals on which our physical, mental, emotional and spiritual being

00:19:59.700 --> 00:20:07.740
rests or is nourished. So immediately you know basically what's wrong with you and you know yourself, nobody has to tell you.

00:20:10.720 --> 00:20:17.000
Now supposing, somebody is very much conditioned so his chakra,

00:20:17.420 --> 00:20:24.420
at the back side, goes off. Now, if you tell that person, "You are a conditioned person," he'll not like it

00:20:25.380 --> 00:20:32.300
but he himself, after realization, will say, "Mother, please solve my problem of the back Agnya," means there's some conditioning -

00:20:33.340 --> 00:20:36.400
could be coming from anything.

00:20:40.500 --> 00:20:44.600
And you face yourself directly.

00:20:45.340 --> 00:20:52.400
You don't have to, sort of, sit down and analyze yourself but you just see it clearly on your centers

00:20:52.640 --> 00:20:57.700
what's wrong  with you and if you can relate one center,

00:20:58.860 --> 00:21:02.020
another center, the combinations of these centers

00:21:02.300 --> 00:21:07.780
and actually what is the matter with you, immediately you will know what's the problem is.

00:21:11.700 --> 00:21:19.100
so you know the Absolute Truth. Now you have known from India many people have come as false

00:21:19.380 --> 00:21:26.040
gurus and everybody tells Me about them; They are just here to make money. These are

00:21:28.320 --> 00:21:35.780
quite a camouflage they have but still with realization you immediately know that he is a cheat

00:21:37.660 --> 00:21:43.740
or he's a demon, demonic person - you have to just put your hands like this and you can feel it -

00:21:46.320 --> 00:21:54.060
the vibrations which are not pulsations of tremor or anything but cool

00:21:54.300 --> 00:22:01.040
breeze like things that flow, suddenly becomes hot. Sometimes they might create a little blister also

00:22:01.660 --> 00:22:08.480
