01:28:47.600 --> 01:28:53.920
Now please take down your hands. Please open your eyes.

01:28:55.300 --> 01:28:58.300
Put your hands towards Me like this

01:28:59.440 --> 01:29:04.540
and watch Me without thinking. Watch Me without thinking.

01:29:13.420 --> 01:29:19.780
Now please, put the right hand towards Me like this, put down your head

01:29:20.220 --> 01:29:26.620
and see for yourself, if there is a cool or a warm or hot

01:29:27.540 --> 01:29:33.540
air like waves, breeze is coming out of

01:29:33.780 --> 01:29:39.600
your fontanel bone area. Now don't put your hand on top of your head

01:29:40.020 --> 01:29:45.780
but away from it and see for yourself, if there is a cool breeze coming

01:29:46.320 --> 01:29:53.020
or a warm breeze or some sort of a hot breeze is coming

01:29:53.240 --> 01:29:57.500
out of your own head. Some people get it little far away.

01:30:00.480 --> 01:30:08.040
Now, with the left hand, now you put it towards Me, like this. Now put down your

01:30:08.320 --> 01:30:13.380
head again, please and see for yourself, if there is,

01:30:14.440 --> 01:30:20.320
if there is, a cool or a warm or a hot

01:30:20.680 --> 01:30:27.480
breeze coming like waves out of your own fontanel bone area.

01:30:32.140 --> 01:30:36.720
Now again once with your right hand. Please

01:30:39.640 --> 01:30:45.800
put down your head and see for yourself, if there is

01:30:46.040 --> 01:30:52.720
cool, warm or hot breeze coming

01:30:53.140 --> 01:31:01.020
out of your fontanel bone area. If it is hot, means you have not forgiven

01:31:02.360 --> 01:31:10.340
Please forgive, now please forgive everyone - you are not going to miss your Self-realization.

01:31:12.980 --> 01:31:15.980
Alright.

01:31:18.580 --> 01:31:25.340
Keep away from the head. If you keep on top, you won't feel. Now, please put both the hands towards the sky

01:31:25.620 --> 01:31:29.480
and push back your head and here

01:31:37.440 --> 01:31:45.360
you ask a question three times. One question you ask three times;

01:31:46.220 --> 01:31:50.120
Anyone of these three questions which I tell you.

01:31:52.240 --> 01:31:59.100
"Mother, is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?" "Mother, is this the

01:32:00.700 --> 01:32:07.540
All-Pervading Power of God's love?" or "Mother, is this the Param Chaitanya?"

01:32:07.760 --> 01:32:14.160
Ask anyone of these questions three times.

01:32:21.300 --> 01:32:26.780
Now, please put down your heads, put down your hands.

01:32:28.480 --> 01:32:32.280
Now, put both the hands towards Me like this.

01:32:35.600 --> 01:32:43.180
Those who have felt cool, warm or hot breeze out of their fontanel bone area

01:32:43.620 --> 01:32:50.520
or on their finger-tips or on their hands, please raise both your hands.

01:32:55.240 --> 01:33:00.600
Ahhh, you got it all of you! May God bless you!

01:33:01.800 --> 01:33:07.540
May God... This is what you are feeling for the first time this All-Pervading power - first time.

01:33:09.120 --> 01:33:14.260
First time you are feeling. You have never felt it before. I bow to you,

01:33:14.600 --> 01:33:19.880
to all of you now, your saintly life has started but I again and again request you

01:33:21.000 --> 01:33:28.960
that whenever I'm there, there are crowds and many people come in but there are very few who really try to become

01:33:29.660 --> 01:33:35.180
what they have to become. Sahaja yoga cannot be a certificate - it's a becoming.

01:33:35.640 --> 01:33:41.120
It's very important at this time of evolutionary phase that we are in,

01:33:41.520 --> 01:33:44.600
is a great responsibility upon all of us,

01:33:46.280 --> 01:33:50.240
to become the Spirit and transform the whole world.

01:33:51.320 --> 01:33:57.100
and help the whole world to solve it's problems. May God bless you all!

01:33:59.760 --> 01:34:04.380
[APPLAUSE]

01:34:04.720 --> 01:34:09.640
[APPLAUSE]

01:34:17.680 --> 01:34:24.920
Like yesterday, all those who have not felt, can come on this side but I'll take your leave, if you don't mind.

01:34:25.380 --> 01:34:28.720
I've to do some cooking for sahaja yogis today.

01:34:31.460 --> 01:34:39.120
When you leave the hall, there is a pamphlet here which tells you about the follow-up program here in the Town Hall

01:34:39.820 --> 01:34:46.020
on Friday, the 6th of March 7:30pm, in the lower Town Hall - the Peace Hall.

01:34:47.320 --> 01:34:52.880
It also has information on various centers around Sydney

01:34:53.240 --> 01:34:57.700
so if you want more information or you want to proceed with what you received tonight,

01:34:58.040 --> 01:35:02.800
there are many people, in many districts, who can give you a hand to do so.

01:35:03.460 --> 01:35:08.220
So this you find at the entrance you came in.
